title: 820-3662 fan spins no BIOS no CPU
message:
Board was liquid damaged. From a shop was already UC'ed
No visibles.

Fan spins up.
No light on USB mouse
CPU does not get hot.

PPVCC_S0_CPU 1.7v
green / orange MagSafe

title: 820-3662 fan spins no BIOS no CPU
message: Yeah, good luck with that one.....Inspect closely if you can find corrosion evidence. Could very well be an already dead CPU as is so common on these.
